reviewText: My son loves these DVDs ! we have watched all of them plus they each have some extra shows we've never seen or heard of!!
Low price, super fast shipping and product arrived in excellent condition! A++++++
I can't wait to see these! I can't believe I only paid $35 for five DVDs!! The other listings priced this box (or similar)'at $125!
Came wrapped in orginal packaging. Exactly what I expected. Thanks!
